HEADWORD: Peignoir
<hw>Pei`gnoir"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>peigner</ets> to comb, L. <ets>pectinare</ets>. See
<er>Pectinate</er>.]</ety> <def>A woman's loose dressing sack; hence, a
